(10817, 'Spironolactone (delta) 25mg 10 tab', 'سبيرونولاكتون 25مجم 10 اقراص', '', '3', 'Spironolactone', 'Global napi pharmaceuticals > al delta pharmaceuticals trading co.', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مدر للبول', 'Diuretic.potassium-sparing diuretics', '25mg', 'Spironolactone is indicated for the treatment of the following conditions:
